import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import '../styles/scss/theme.scss';
import t from '../i18n';
import { PropsTable, Playground } from 'docz'
import { Label } from './index';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"entry-label"}}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="h1">{`Entry Label`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>

<PropsTable of={Label} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"label"}}>{`Label`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"exemplos"}}>{`Exemplos`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Label>{t\`common.label\`}</Label>
<Label htmlFor="rotulo">{t\`common.label\`} </Label>`} __scope={{props,t,Label}}>
    <Label>{t`common.label`}</Label>
<Label htmlFor='rotulo'>{t`common.label`} </Label>
</Playground></MDXTag>
